subsection.p:
          To obtain a ComponentFinder we can:
          




                create a new ComponentFinder that has access to all the GUI 
                components in the AWT hierarchy:
                
ComponentFinder finder = ComponentFinder.finderWithCurrentAwtHierarchy();
              
            




                create a new ComponentFinder that only has access to the GUI components
                created behind it:
                
ComponentFinder finder = ComponentFinder.finderWithNewAwtHierarchy();
              
            




                use the existing ComponentFinder from a RobotFixture: 
                
// assuming robot is a RobotFixture 
ComponentFinder finder = robot.finder();
